1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 6=

4
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,080
Thank you all

5
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:52,800
for coming today

6
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:54,880
to the final exhibition
curated by my father.

7
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:57,960
Even though he's gone,

8
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,880
the art he loved

9
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,680
will live on.

10
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,800
Let's all move over this way.

11
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,800
Everyone, please stay a moment.

12
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,320
I know

13
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:13,520
you were all my father's
closest friends.

14
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:15,800
So before we begin,

15
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,800
we've prepared something special.

16
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:20,520
Let's honor his memory through art.

17
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:23,080
We hope everyone will
leave a few brushstrokes

18
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,240
in his memory.

19
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,120
Xiaomi,

20
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,720
are you happy

21
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:28,960
with my arrangement?

22
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,680
In that case,

23
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,960
let's invite the new owner
of Comic gallery

24
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:37,360
to give us the first painting.

25
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:38,120
Come on.

26
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,040
Paint something for us.

27
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:39,680
I...

28
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,280
She used to be an award-winning artist.

29
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:41,920
Really.

30
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,200
Please, Miss Qiao.

31
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:45,800
Go ahead.

32
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:48,080
Our genius artist.

33
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,320
I wonder what she'll paint.

34
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,440
Xiaomi.

35
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,160
Let's see what you've got.

36
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,320
What, too shy to show off?

37
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,080
Don't tell me amnesia

38
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:59,360
made her forget how to paint too.

39
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,080
Xiaomi,

40
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,680
Dad's watching over you.

41
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,040
Is she nervous?

42
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:15,920
Just paint something.

43
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,200
(Dad.)

44
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,680
(I really can't paint anymore.)

45
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,200
(But why?)

46
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,320
(Why did losing my memory)

47
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,600
(make me forget how to paint too?)

48
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,800
It's okay.

49
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,680
Trust me.

50
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:12,600
I'm sorry. I'm late.

51
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,840
I've come back to marry you.

52
00:03:15,340 --> 00:03:15,910
(Qin Yu... my fiancé?)

53
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:17,280
(Qin Yu... my fiancé?)
I'm your fiancé.

54
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:17,640
(Qin Yu... my fiancé?)

55
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,520
Go ahead.

56
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,720
Tell me first.

57
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,320
Why did you suddenly

58
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,640
want me to paint you?

59
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,560
What's wrong with wanting
to preserve my beauty?

60
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,560
Miss Qiao,

61
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,560
I believe I told you before.

62
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,640
I don't come cheap.

63
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:03,760
Name your price.

64
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,720
I can afford it.

65
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,760
One

66
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,400
voluntary kiss.

67
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,280
Deal?

68
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:17,960
Scared?

69
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,800
Just kidding.

70
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,920
I love painting.

71
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:22,760
And my favorite thing to paint
has always been you.

72
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:23,960
Enough talk.

73
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,200
Let's get started.

74
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,120
Would you mind taking off your jacket?

75
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,680
I'd rather not.

76
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,880
Miss Qiao,

77
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,160
time to pay up.

78
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:42,920
I...

79
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,080
Put it on my tab for now.

80
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,080
I'm going to change first.

81
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,560
Xiaomi,

82
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,280
just like you asked,

83
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,440
all the paintings we kept off display

84
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:11,080
and the ones gathering
dust in storage are here.

85
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,600
What are you up to?

86
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,640
Catching a thief.

87
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,320
I'm fine. Don't worry about me.

88
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:16,200
Just go home.

89
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,020
(Qin Yu)

90
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:39,440
(It really was him.)

91
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:42,040
(He really painted my portrait.)

92
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,280
(Qiao Zhiwei was lying after all.)

93
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,960
How did you get in here?

94
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:00,920
Do you remember the day
I painted this portrait of you?

95
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,040
It was your 19th birthday.

96
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,440
You said

97
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,480
if it snowed in September,

98
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,440
you'd believe in miracles.

99
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,640
Don't you want to know
what else happened that day?

100
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,560
Not interested.

101
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,240
Stop pretending.

102
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,880
You're sweating.

103
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,360
Seeing me

104
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,360
has you all flustered, hasn't it?

105
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,720
The AC's broken.

106
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,480
Idiot.

107
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,760
Do you really have

108
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:51,160
no interest in our past at all?

109
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,240
Get out of my company.

110
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,760
Or I'll call the cops.

111
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,440
It's getting late.

112
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,440
You should head home.

113
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:10,640
If you still want
to believe in miracles,

114
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,240
come with me.

115
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,840
Qin Yu!

116
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,760
Do you know how annoying you are?

117
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,120
Don't try that on me.

118
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,440
Look up.

119
00:09:45,810 --> 00:09:47,920
♪We say good morning,
we say good night♪

120
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:51,100
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

121
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,280
I know what you're afraid of.

122
00:09:54,830 --> 00:09:56,400
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

123
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,560
But you have me.

124
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,880
From now on,

125
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:00,800
♪Let me go, set me free♪

126
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:02,320
you'll have nothing to be afraid of.

127
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:05,920
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

128
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:11,760
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

129
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,800
♪The freedom you gave me♪

130
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:19,360
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

131
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:22,960
♪Love can barely move forward♪

132
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:26,720
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

133
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:30,120
♪The closeness I long for♪

134
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:34,840
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

135
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,600
♪I don't want to break free♪

136
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:41,960
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

137
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,880
Move the story along.

138
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,680
Cut the cheesy romance act.

139
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,720
Or you know the consequences.

140
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,480
I'm the main character.

141
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,240
How the story unfolds,

142
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:10,920
I call the shots.

143
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,640
Even if the fire was an accident,

144
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,960
what about Ye Xiaoduo's miserable life?

145
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,120
You caused all of it.

146
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:32,720
Could I be the killer?

147
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,840
How do you know you're not?

148
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,440
Liar.

149
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:37,960
Sc*mbag!

150
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,920
Qin Yu,

151
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,040
what the hell are you doing?

152
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:46,600
You've actually
fallen for Xiaomi,

153
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:47,720
haven't you?

154
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,800
So you think

155
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,800
I'm the one who should die.

156
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,240
Right?

157
00:12:12,310 --> 00:12:14,380
♪We say good morning,
we say good night♪

158
00:12:14,380 --> 00:12:17,800
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

159
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:21,290
♪The sweeter it is,
the luckier we seem♪

160
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:25,280
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

161
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:28,380
♪Let me go, set me free♪

162
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:32,420
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

163
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:38,370
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

164
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,860
♪The freedom you gave me♪

165
00:12:41,860 --> 00:12:45,500
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

166
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:49,030
♪Love can barely move forward♪

167
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:52,810
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

168
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:56,150
♪The closeness I long for♪

169
00:12:56,150 --> 00:13:00,540
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

170
00:13:00,950 --> 00:13:02,770
♪I don't want to break free♪

171
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:08,140
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

